Established in the year 1989, we, Ganesh Corporation, are a reputed organization engaged in manufacturing, supplying & exporting a unparalleled range of Stainless Steel Wire Mesh Filter, Sandwich Type Circular Screen Pack, Sandwich Type Candle Filter Pack, Dutch Weave Mesh, Kidney Shaped & Disk Filter, Hopper Magnet and many more.

Our Team: Our organization is assisted by a dexterous team of professionals, who are considered as the backbone of our firm.

Our Quality: Our organization pay great importance towards the quality of the products being offered by us. Owing to this, all the products are manufactured in accordance with the industry set quality parameters without any compromise with the quality.

Our Infrastructure: Our organization has established a state-of-the-art infrastructure facility which sprawls over a vast area of land.

Clients Satisfaction: Our organization is one of the recognized organization engaged in offering a wide range of Stainless Steel Wire Mesh Filter, Sandwich Type Circular Screen Pack, Sandwich Type Candle Filter Pack, Dutch Weave Mesh and many more.
